e387fdc676fd241a988baf9c","tid":1999117,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:04:04.000Z","msg":"現時亦有<strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">5位年青手足</span></ins></strong>已被判入<ins><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">勞教中心/更新中心</span></strong></ins>，相信大家都唔係好知係咩嚟，其實呢幾位手足受緊嘅不但係牢獄之苦，仲會俾懲教狗<strong><ins>肉體同精神虐待</ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">咩係勞教中心？</span></span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【同囚・上】徒手洗廁、捧糞 前少年犯憶勞教生活：第二晚已想死</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社區專題/98516/同囚-上-徒手洗廁-捧糞-前少年犯憶勞教生活-第二晚已想死\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%2F98516%2F%E5%90%8C%E5%9B%9A-%E4%B8%8A-%E5%BE%92%E6%89%8B%E6%B4%97%E5%BB%81-%E6%8D%A7%E7%B3%9E-%E5%89%8D%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E7%8A%AF%E6%86%B6%E5%8B%9E%E6%95%99%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB-%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%99%9A%E5%B7%B2%E6%83%B3%E6%AD%BB&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgktjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=1f07da9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社區專題/98516/同囚-上-徒手洗廁-捧糞-前少年犯憶勞教生活-第二晚已想死</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>《同囚》預告片</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kdb1chbnwwc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dkdb1chbnwwc&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgktjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=38b32a1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kdb1chbnwwc</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>勞教中心</ins></strong><br />\n勞教中心是代替監禁的其中一種刑罰，但只適用於14至24歲的男性犯人。勞教中心著重透過嚴格紀律及勞動工作，在短時間內為犯人帶來沖擊，從而提醒他們不可再犯案。勞教中心令不適用於曾經被判監禁或判入教導所的犯人。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署署長會考慮犯人在勞教中心的紀律，決定犯人的羈留時期。14至20歲的犯人，最少會被羈留 1 個月、最多則可被羈留6個月； 21至24歲的犯人，可被羈留3個月至12個月。<br />\n<br />\n犯人獲釋後，可能要再接受為期一年的監管，期間要遵守某些規限，例如在晚上某個時間過後，必須要留在家中。犯人若不遵從監管條件，可能會再被送入勞教中心。"},{"pid":"2c66ff7cce4b10916d946acbc45dc34c0c1e16df","tid":1999117,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"希望大家下個禮拜可以繼續聲援，每日幾十單手足案件，<br />\n去聽審聲援嘅，嚟嚟去去都係個幾十人，<br />\n公衆席好多時候都坐唔悶，<br />\n試想像你喺手足，你會點諗？<br />\n<br />\n200萬人，<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">每人1年花半日去聽審聲援手足</span></ins></strong>，我相信唔係好苛刻啫係咪？"},{"pid":"96141c28c15a24c266b013a0a8c06cedefec1801","tid":1999117,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:04:49.000Z","msg":"自推10連<br />\n1<br />\n<br />\n手足需要大家，<br />\n請聽審聲援手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425ad05a11d9238ad2cf0af6f4c8fea91ad064aa","tid":1999117,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"自推10連<br />\n2<br />\n<br />\n手足需要大家，<br />\n請聽審聲援手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a68ab9d1f0cae7a31fea8c1bbf8f8f0f63dab46","tid":1999117,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"自推10連<br />\n3<br />\n<br />\n手足需要大家，<br />\n請聽審聲援手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9812b6da3f32f3200294b4976b6c026888d210","tid":1999117,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:06:56.000Z"